::Battera::

She looked as the lights in her room flickered on and off.  She had a 
gut feeling something was up.  She got up and went to her room door.  
She went to open it and stopped.  She turned around and sat back down 
in her chair. "No, they wouldn't want a Pred to help them."  She 
sighed and hoped that what ever was wrng wold soon be cleared up.
